WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:15.400

00:01:59.985 --> 00:02:01.105
These past couple of years,

00:02:01.185 --> 00:02:03.105
influencers have been
flocking to Yuanlongli,

00:02:03.185 --> 00:02:04.145
especially the 18th floor.

00:02:04.825 --> 00:02:08.345
Lots of youngsters
sneak in to shoot videos

00:02:08.425 --> 00:02:10.625
or do some urban exploration stuff.

00:02:14.465 --> 00:02:19.065
Which means the missing child
came here to film too?

00:02:22.865 --> 00:02:23.705
Yes.

00:02:27.025 --> 00:02:29.025
So we need to search this place carefully.

00:02:39.185 --> 00:02:40.505
Han Zi'ang!

00:02:42.105 --> 00:02:43.385
Han Zi'ang!

00:02:44.385 --> 00:02:46.265
Your mom wants you home.

00:02:55.465 --> 00:02:56.745
Never seen this before?

00:02:58.065 --> 00:03:00.185
Look at mine. An upgraded version.

00:03:04.505 --> 00:03:06.345
Safer.

00:03:12.145 --> 00:03:15.265
Can your upgrade block the sun as well?

00:03:15.345 --> 00:03:16.945
Stop hiding.

00:03:17.905 --> 00:03:19.385
Your mom wants you back.

00:03:20.385 --> 00:03:21.265
Han Zi'ang!

00:03:35.825 --> 00:03:36.825
Han Zi'ang.

00:03:37.545 --> 00:03:39.345
I see you. Come out.

00:03:46.745 --> 00:03:49.065
BY THE ANCIENT IMMORTAL
ALL EVIL IS QUELLED

00:03:49.665 --> 00:03:50.585
What's that?

00:03:50.665 --> 00:03:52.465
Customized by Yuanlongli.

00:03:52.985 --> 00:03:54.305
More effective than police tape.

00:03:55.585 --> 00:03:59.065
Say, do you remember this unit?

00:03:59.145 --> 00:04:01.945
That case started here.

00:04:02.545 --> 00:04:04.345
The black robe. Remember?

00:04:10.065 --> 00:04:14.185
Sir, we should focus on
finding that kid first.

00:04:15.665 --> 00:04:17.745
Shame. It became a cold case.

00:04:19.865 --> 00:04:21.504
Nothing to regret.

00:04:21.585 --> 00:04:25.305
And it's not a cold case.
It was mishandled.

00:04:26.505 --> 00:04:28.985
Don't talk nonsense.
How was it mishandled?

00:04:30.025 --> 00:04:31.225
Did you forget?

00:04:31.745 --> 00:04:38.025
That case was the reason I left Weiyang
and transferred to teach in Beijing.

00:04:41.185 --> 00:04:43.065
I wasn't cut out to be a detective.

00:04:43.145 --> 00:04:45.385
Stop talking like that.
Who says you're not?

00:04:45.465 --> 00:04:47.865
If I say you are, then you are.

00:04:53.065 --> 00:04:53.945
Sir,

00:04:55.065 --> 00:04:57.625
did you bring me here to find the kid?

00:04:58.265 --> 00:04:59.105
Or for something else?

00:05:02.305 --> 00:05:04.025
What else would it be?

00:05:04.105 --> 00:05:07.105
Come on. Let's check this floor.

00:05:09.425 --> 00:05:10.585
Han Zi'ang!

00:05:12.305 --> 00:05:13.385
Come out!

00:05:15.185 --> 00:05:16.185
Han Zi'ang!

00:05:16.265 --> 00:05:18.505
BY THE ANCIENT IMMORTAL
ALL EVIL IS QUELLED

00:05:29.545 --> 00:05:31.825
-Here he comes.
-He's here.

00:05:34.625 --> 00:05:35.465
ROUTE 11
TRAIN STATION TO WORKERS' COMMUNITY

00:05:35.545 --> 00:05:36.505
We're here.

00:05:43.425 --> 00:05:45.865
-About the same height, right?
-Right.

00:05:45.945 --> 00:05:47.905
Put them up where people pass by.

00:05:47.985 --> 00:05:50.425
Make them clearly visible. Split up.

00:05:50.505 --> 00:05:51.585
Don't waste any of this.

00:05:51.665 --> 00:05:53.265
There's a reward if anyone finds him.

00:05:53.345 --> 00:05:55.345
-Got it, Officer He.
-Share these among yourselves.

00:06:01.545 --> 00:06:04.625
Liangfen for sale! Fresh liangfen!

00:06:08.505 --> 00:06:10.105
BE A CIVILIZED NEIGHBOR
AND BUILD A BETTER COMMUNITY

00:06:20.745 --> 00:06:21.905
Hand these out.

00:06:25.385 --> 00:06:26.305
MISSING PERSONS

00:06:28.385 --> 00:06:30.225
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

00:06:30.305 --> 00:06:32.945
MISSING PERSONS

00:06:33.025 --> 00:06:34.465
The contact numbers are on there.

00:06:34.545 --> 00:06:35.465
Call this number.

00:06:41.545 --> 00:06:42.545
How about this?

00:06:42.625 --> 00:06:44.025
Longhair.

00:06:44.105 --> 00:06:45.625
-My goodness!
-Good lord!

00:06:46.385 --> 00:06:47.825
-Run quickly!
-Run!

00:06:47.905 --> 00:06:50.425
Get back here! Stand still!

00:06:51.945 --> 00:06:53.985
Longhair! Get back!

00:06:59.625 --> 00:07:00.985
Get back!

00:07:07.185 --> 00:07:08.185
Playing big, huh?

00:07:10.145 --> 00:07:11.105
Only a quarter of a yuan.

00:07:11.785 --> 00:07:12.665
Cut it out.

00:07:17.065 --> 00:07:18.065
Take a look at this.

00:07:18.665 --> 00:07:19.825
Do you recognize them?

00:07:21.145 --> 00:07:22.865
MISSING PERSONS

00:07:25.985 --> 00:07:27.745
No. I haven't seen them.

00:07:28.585 --> 00:07:31.385
-No.
-We don't know.

00:07:32.465 --> 00:07:33.665
Alright.

00:07:34.465 --> 00:07:36.705
In that case, keep an eye out.

00:07:36.785 --> 00:07:37.905
Sure.

00:07:37.985 --> 00:07:39.065
Answer!

00:07:39.145 --> 00:07:41.025
Of course.

00:07:44.105 --> 00:07:46.985
We'll take care of it.
Don't worry, Officer He.

00:07:48.865 --> 00:07:50.025
Careful.

00:07:54.865 --> 00:07:56.585
Smile.

00:07:57.385 --> 00:07:59.065
-Make it quick.
-No problem.

00:08:00.145 --> 00:08:01.705
Please drive safely, Officer He.

00:08:04.425 --> 00:08:05.625
Take care.

00:08:09.385 --> 00:08:10.825
KIOSK

00:08:15.265 --> 00:08:18.545
Page this number. 1276165888.

00:08:18.625 --> 00:08:20.785
"Mr. Jin. Urgent. Call me back
as soon as possible."

00:08:23.265 --> 00:08:25.545
"Urgent. Call me back
as soon as possible."

00:08:25.625 --> 00:08:26.865
LIKE GENERAL STORE

00:08:26.945 --> 00:08:28.625
Hong Kong, China, has been handed back.

00:08:28.705 --> 00:08:29.545
BUSINESS TRANSFORMATION

00:08:29.625 --> 00:08:32.225
We need to keep up with the times.

00:08:32.745 --> 00:08:36.784
From now on, everything
runs on a business line.

00:08:36.865 --> 00:08:39.904
What are our core businesses?

00:08:41.465 --> 00:08:44.065
-You tell me.
-They are loansharking,

00:08:44.144 --> 00:08:47.025
debt collection, hair salons,
and protection fees.

00:08:49.185 --> 00:08:50.305
Get lost.

00:08:50.945 --> 00:08:53.585
You trained all day,
and that's what you learned?

00:08:53.665 --> 00:08:56.545
That's called public management.

00:08:56.625 --> 00:08:58.505
Public management!

00:08:58.585 --> 00:08:59.945
Loansharking?

00:09:00.025 --> 00:09:02.065
Mr. Jin.

00:09:02.145 --> 00:09:04.145
Why didn't you return the page?

00:09:04.225 --> 00:09:05.665
Something has happened.

00:09:05.745 --> 00:09:08.225
MAY WEALTH FLOW YOUR WAY

00:09:08.305 --> 00:09:10.265
MISSING PERSONS

00:09:10.345 --> 00:09:12.825
Manlang was in Yuanlongli yesterday?

00:09:12.905 --> 00:09:17.225
Yeah. Wolf told me himself last night.

00:09:17.945 --> 00:09:21.105
I saw two bloodstained clothes in his bag.

00:09:24.425 --> 00:09:26.905
-No wonder he skipped training.
-Tell me about it.

00:09:28.825 --> 00:09:30.425
-Wolf is here.
-That rascal!

00:09:32.225 --> 00:09:33.825
Mr. Jin.

00:09:33.905 --> 00:09:35.065
Please…

00:09:35.145 --> 00:09:36.865
Where have you been?

00:10:02.025 --> 00:10:04.585
Officer He. No one has seen her.

00:10:09.785 --> 00:10:11.505
You can teleport now?

00:10:12.025 --> 00:10:13.505
You were at the snack street just now,

00:10:13.585 --> 00:10:15.385
and now you're at Jinsha Market.

00:10:15.465 --> 00:10:17.385
-Came to tip him off?
-Officer He,

00:10:18.145 --> 00:10:19.825
he's here for training.

00:10:20.345 --> 00:10:21.545
We've restructured.

00:10:22.225 --> 00:10:24.505
We don't break the law anymore.

00:10:25.425 --> 00:10:28.625
Jin Manshan, do you believe that yourself?

00:10:29.385 --> 00:10:30.785
If you don't believe me, ask them.

00:10:31.865 --> 00:10:35.385
What are our four main sectors?

00:10:35.465 --> 00:10:39.225
-Public management.
-Public management.

00:10:39.305 --> 00:10:42.505
-High-risk finance.
-High-risk finance.

00:10:42.585 --> 00:10:46.105
-Security services.
-Security services.

00:10:46.185 --> 00:10:50.825
-Beauty and wellness.
-Beauty and wellness.

00:11:05.905 --> 00:11:06.945
Fine.

00:11:07.985 --> 00:11:10.105
Since you've got people here,
I'll leave this with you.

00:11:10.185 --> 00:11:11.505
-Ask around for me.
-No problem.

00:11:15.785 --> 00:11:16.625
Where's your brother?

00:11:17.865 --> 00:11:18.945
Jin Manlang?

00:11:20.745 --> 00:11:22.025
He went to buy training materials.

00:11:43.625 --> 00:11:46.025
LOUNGE

00:11:56.825 --> 00:11:59.425
REMITTANCE NOTICE, AMOUNT: 12,000 YUAN

00:12:32.025 --> 00:12:35.945
FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT. DO NOT IMITATE

00:13:38.025 --> 00:13:40.105
Yuanlongli

00:13:40.185 --> 00:13:42.345
Eighteenth floor

00:13:42.425 --> 00:13:46.065
Eighteenth floor with 18 pillars

00:13:46.145 --> 00:13:50.305
Eighteen bodies, 18 heads

00:13:51.305 --> 00:13:54.745
Kids, who taught you that rhyme?

00:13:56.225 --> 00:13:59.185
Whoever tells me gets chocolate.

00:13:59.265 --> 00:14:01.185
-A classmate!
-An old man!

00:14:01.265 --> 00:14:03.585
One at a time, please.
Who taught you that?

00:14:09.825 --> 00:14:14.345
Officer, are you here about
the two people who went missing upstairs?

00:14:18.705 --> 00:14:20.265
I'm really sorry.

00:14:20.785 --> 00:14:22.665
Should I take you to the hospital?

00:14:22.745 --> 00:14:24.105
It's fine. No need.

00:14:24.185 --> 00:14:25.185
We're here.

00:14:37.465 --> 00:14:39.665
Maybe you can come in and wash up.

00:14:42.905 --> 00:14:44.345
I've got slippers.

00:15:07.545 --> 00:15:09.865
This towel is new. Never used.

00:15:10.825 --> 00:15:13.585
The bathroom is right behind you.

00:15:14.945 --> 00:15:16.145
Thank you.

00:15:21.065 --> 00:15:22.145
Wait…

00:16:00.705 --> 00:16:02.665
-Thank you.
-It's nothing.

00:16:24.385 --> 00:16:25.745
I have some gauze here.

00:16:25.825 --> 00:16:27.585
Want me to help?

00:16:30.385 --> 00:16:31.865
Oh… Sure.

00:16:44.865 --> 00:16:45.905
Hold still.

00:16:59.265 --> 00:17:00.385
You can keep the slippers.

00:17:10.625 --> 00:17:13.585
By the way, I'm Ran Fangxu.

00:17:14.745 --> 00:17:16.105
I'm Qiao Suqing.

00:17:41.065 --> 00:17:42.545
MISSING PERSONS

00:17:56.625 --> 00:17:57.785
Sorry about that.

00:18:23.865 --> 00:18:25.305
You little brat.

00:18:25.385 --> 00:18:27.585
You're talking nonsense again.
Watch your mouth.

00:18:27.665 --> 00:18:30.065
Silly boy! All that
for a piece of chocolate?

00:18:31.425 --> 00:18:32.305
Don't hit him.

00:18:33.185 --> 00:18:34.425
What's going on?

00:18:34.505 --> 00:18:36.185
Why did you teach him that rhyme?

00:18:36.265 --> 00:18:37.825
I didn't want to.

00:18:42.385 --> 00:18:44.585
This morning, I picked up
a flyer by the roadside.

00:18:44.665 --> 00:18:46.225
That rhyme was printed on it.

00:18:46.305 --> 00:18:48.185
It said if you don't pass it on,
there'll be bloodshed.

00:18:48.265 --> 00:18:49.425
That's nonsense.

00:18:49.505 --> 00:18:50.945
It's real.

00:18:51.025 --> 00:18:52.385
I'm not making it up.

00:18:52.905 --> 00:18:54.625
This morning, right when
I opened the door,

00:18:54.705 --> 00:18:56.185
something bad happened.

00:18:56.705 --> 00:18:58.345
There was someone…

00:19:06.305 --> 00:19:07.305
Someone?

00:19:07.385 --> 00:19:09.425
No one. I remembered it wrong.

00:19:11.825 --> 00:19:14.145
Don't be scared.
I'm in charge around here.

00:19:14.225 --> 00:19:17.105
Stop asking. I can't remember.

00:19:20.785 --> 00:19:22.345
HE

00:19:22.985 --> 00:19:25.745
Ma'am, if anything
comes back to you, page me.

00:19:25.825 --> 00:19:26.785
Okay.

00:19:40.185 --> 00:19:41.345
Officer,

00:19:41.865 --> 00:19:43.625
I recognize that person.

00:19:43.705 --> 00:19:46.065
He had a bag too.
There was a lot of blood inside.

00:19:48.385 --> 00:19:49.905
Who was it? Tell me.

00:19:49.985 --> 00:19:52.345
Then I want another chocolate.

00:20:19.625 --> 00:20:20.905
Rooftop?

00:21:04.425 --> 00:21:06.105
PATTIA CLUB, THAI MASSAGE

00:21:27.105 --> 00:21:29.145
FIRE EXTINGUISHER

00:22:18.985 --> 00:22:23.105
YUXI CIGARETTE

00:22:23.185 --> 00:22:24.785
Flip-top Yuxi cigarettes.

00:22:25.385 --> 00:22:28.105
Mainly for bosses.
Twenty yuan for one packet.

00:22:43.185 --> 00:22:44.905
FIRE EXTINGUISHER

00:23:11.305 --> 00:23:15.745
01: I HAVE KEY INFORMATION
ABOUT THE YUANLONGLI CASE

00:23:34.665 --> 00:23:36.185
Hello, 126?

00:23:37.185 --> 00:23:38.785
Please page this number again.

00:23:38.865 --> 00:23:41.305
8233585.

00:23:42.545 --> 00:23:43.865
Page it ten times.

00:23:44.385 --> 00:23:45.425
Leave a message.

00:23:46.065 --> 00:23:49.625
"I have key information
about the Yuanlongli case.

00:23:50.385 --> 00:23:54.305
Come to Number 407, New York Block.

00:23:54.385 --> 00:23:55.505
As soon as possible."

00:23:57.345 --> 00:23:59.185
Please page it ten times.

00:24:00.265 --> 00:24:01.145
Thanks.

00:24:25.385 --> 00:24:27.905
01: I HAVE KEY INFORMATION
ABOUT THE YUANLONGLI CASE

00:24:56.385 --> 00:24:57.545
Are you okay?

00:25:07.145 --> 00:25:08.425
RAN FANGXU'S ID

00:25:10.545 --> 00:25:11.865
Don't be nervous.

00:25:11.945 --> 00:25:12.785
If you're hurt,

00:25:12.865 --> 00:25:14.945
come find me at the criminal department
of the Nanshan Branch.

00:25:15.025 --> 00:25:16.305
The name is Ran Fangxu.

00:25:19.905 --> 00:25:20.945
I'm really sorry.

00:25:25.065 --> 00:25:26.225
Qiao.

00:25:26.305 --> 00:25:28.105
Can I borrow your phone?

00:25:35.305 --> 00:25:37.545
There's a group fight
at Qingsong Cement Factory.

00:25:37.625 --> 00:25:39.465
The whole squad's gone. No one left.

00:25:40.505 --> 00:25:41.585
Oh, right.

00:25:41.665 --> 00:25:43.345
He Yuanhang should be free.

00:25:43.425 --> 00:25:44.945
You can try calling him.

00:25:45.465 --> 00:25:46.745
Alright.

00:25:54.785 --> 00:25:57.945
The top two floors were rented
by a big boss a couple of years ago.

00:25:58.025 --> 00:26:00.465
He secretly turned
the 18th floor into a club.

00:26:01.705 --> 00:26:05.105
Half of the 17th floor was staff dorms.

00:26:05.185 --> 00:26:07.585
The other half was rented out.

00:26:08.185 --> 00:26:09.505
Earlier this year, there was
a nationwide crackdown on prostitution.

00:26:10.105 --> 00:26:12.225
Someone reported the 18th floor,

00:26:12.305 --> 00:26:13.585
and it's been shut since.

00:26:14.185 --> 00:26:15.625
Then what's with this door?

00:26:15.705 --> 00:26:18.905
Before, drunk customers used
to climb out to the rooftop from here.

00:26:18.985 --> 00:26:21.345
We were worried about accidents,
so we made it a hidden door.

00:26:21.425 --> 00:26:22.625
Why didn't you mention this yesterday?

00:26:22.705 --> 00:26:24.785
Those two couldn't have had a key.

00:26:25.305 --> 00:26:26.345
It's open.

00:26:58.585 --> 00:27:00.025
Officer Ran,

00:27:00.105 --> 00:27:03.265
please don't tell anyone
I brought you to the rooftop.

00:27:03.345 --> 00:27:05.305
Up there is Mr. Ge's territory.

00:27:05.385 --> 00:27:06.825
I can't afford to cross him.

00:27:06.905 --> 00:27:08.665
Does Mr. Ge have a key?

00:27:08.745 --> 00:27:09.905
Let me tell you.

00:27:09.985 --> 00:27:12.745
That old man is Manager Qian's uncle.

00:27:12.825 --> 00:27:16.145
But don't worry. The Qian family
is shrewd and tightfisted.

00:27:16.745 --> 00:27:18.065
He wouldn't lend out the key.

00:27:19.145 --> 00:27:20.345
Alright.

00:27:31.865 --> 00:27:33.065
BEIJING TRAVEL

00:27:55.065 --> 00:27:57.385
YUXI

00:28:08.785 --> 00:28:11.145
RETRIBUTION FOR STEALING CHICKENS

00:28:23.585 --> 00:28:25.385
PUBLIC SECURITY

00:28:26.265 --> 00:28:28.465
Move it. We've got a homicide.

00:28:28.545 --> 00:28:29.465
Stay sharp.

00:28:30.385 --> 00:28:32.065
We've searched the 18th floor.

00:28:32.145 --> 00:28:33.865
What could we have missed?

00:28:33.945 --> 00:28:35.905
Officer Ran is a top graduate of PPSUC.

00:28:35.985 --> 00:28:37.945
If he says there's a lead,
there is one for sure.

00:29:13.185 --> 00:29:14.545
Something big's going down.

00:29:15.145 --> 00:29:17.025
This is where Mr. Ge keeps chickens.

00:29:17.105 --> 00:29:18.105
Where are the chickens?

00:29:18.185 --> 00:29:20.825
That's exactly the problem.

00:29:22.545 --> 00:29:23.505
There's something here.

00:29:26.065 --> 00:29:27.785
Officer Qu, over here.

00:29:32.025 --> 00:29:33.505
You little rascal.

00:29:34.425 --> 00:29:36.625
-I'll beat you to death!
-Don't come closer. I'm a police officer!

00:29:48.625 --> 00:29:50.385
Doubao, come in.

00:29:50.465 --> 00:29:52.945
What took you so long?

00:29:53.025 --> 00:29:56.465
Let go. Let go of my hand.

00:29:56.545 --> 00:29:57.745
Come in, Doubao.

00:29:57.825 --> 00:29:59.265
Why would I go in?

00:29:59.345 --> 00:30:01.705
-Let go.
-I won't!

00:30:01.785 --> 00:30:02.665
Get in here.

00:30:02.745 --> 00:30:04.225
You killed my chickens!

00:30:04.305 --> 00:30:06.505
That's assaulting an officer.
I'm warning you.

00:30:09.145 --> 00:30:10.225
Stop!

00:30:10.865 --> 00:30:12.025
What took you so long?

00:30:12.105 --> 00:30:13.865
I paged you over a dozen times.

00:30:14.945 --> 00:30:16.665
Come with me. I'll tell you.

00:30:23.625 --> 00:30:24.625
Are you

00:30:25.145 --> 00:30:28.185
8233585?

00:30:28.945 --> 00:30:30.545
I came to see you.

00:30:31.265 --> 00:30:32.985
Good.

00:30:33.065 --> 00:30:34.065
I'll be straight with you.

00:30:34.145 --> 00:30:37.625
I don't have much to go on.
I only saw it once.

00:30:37.705 --> 00:30:38.865
You saw it?

00:30:38.945 --> 00:30:40.425
Yeah. I did.

00:30:40.505 --> 00:30:41.625
Clear as day.

00:30:41.705 --> 00:30:43.265
I saw you too.

00:30:43.345 --> 00:30:44.705
Get down!

00:30:44.785 --> 00:30:46.745
Get down! Get down now!

00:30:46.825 --> 00:30:50.545
Once it's cooked,
it goes straight to the table.

00:30:54.465 --> 00:30:55.305
Old man,

00:30:56.345 --> 00:30:57.625
I'm here…

00:30:59.985 --> 00:31:01.585
Open the door! I'm He Yuanhang.

00:31:09.105 --> 00:31:12.265
Sir, I'm here to check the gas.

00:31:12.345 --> 00:31:13.025
WEIYANG GAS

00:31:13.105 --> 00:31:15.705
Gas inspection? It's inside.

00:31:15.785 --> 00:31:16.985
Go check it yourself.

00:31:20.185 --> 00:31:22.345
Officer He, you were looking for me?

00:31:22.425 --> 00:31:23.705
You paged me, didn't you?

00:31:24.305 --> 00:31:26.585
I paged the number
on the missing persons notice.

00:31:26.665 --> 00:31:28.025
That's my number.

00:31:28.105 --> 00:31:29.425
Who were you talking to just now?

00:31:29.505 --> 00:31:31.105
Someone from the gas company.

00:31:31.185 --> 00:31:32.385
Gas company?

00:31:40.105 --> 00:31:42.625
Officer He! It's me! It's me!

00:31:43.585 --> 00:31:44.425
Jin Manlang?

00:31:46.225 --> 00:31:47.625
Punk.

00:31:49.625 --> 00:31:51.465
Are you here to silence them?

00:31:51.545 --> 00:31:52.665
I'm innocent.

00:31:52.745 --> 00:31:53.985
I didn't kill anyone.

00:31:54.065 --> 00:31:55.265
I didn't mean to cover anything up.

00:31:55.345 --> 00:31:56.785
How did you know
I was going to ask about a murder?

00:32:03.385 --> 00:32:04.225
Rascal.

00:32:04.305 --> 00:32:05.625
You screwed this up.

00:32:10.185 --> 00:32:12.825
All 18 chickens had their throats slit,

00:32:12.905 --> 00:32:15.465
and now you're turning it around,
saying I'm the killer?

00:32:16.065 --> 00:32:17.025
Put that down!

00:32:20.945 --> 00:32:22.785
Where are the chickens?

00:32:22.865 --> 00:32:24.305
Eighteen victims.

00:32:24.385 --> 00:32:25.665
All dumped on the rooftop.

00:32:25.745 --> 00:32:27.665
You think I could just
stand by and do nothing?

00:32:36.545 --> 00:32:37.825
What are you waiting for?

00:32:37.905 --> 00:32:39.945
-Secure the evidence now.
-Alright. Move.

00:32:40.825 --> 00:32:41.825
Fangxu.

00:32:43.625 --> 00:32:44.465
Next time something like this happens,

00:32:44.545 --> 00:32:46.625
shouldn't you call in
the criminal department?

00:32:47.225 --> 00:32:48.505
-I…
-I'm not blaming you.

00:32:49.185 --> 00:32:51.425
It's fine if I made a wasted trip.

00:32:51.945 --> 00:32:53.945
I'm just concerned about how others feel.

00:32:54.025 --> 00:32:56.585
After all, everyone showed up
because of you, Officer Ran.

00:32:56.665 --> 00:32:57.505
Right?

00:33:05.345 --> 00:33:06.825
Sorry about that, Officer Qu.

00:33:06.905 --> 00:33:08.545
I caused you trouble.

00:33:09.225 --> 00:33:12.825
But these bloodstains
were likely a smokescreen.

00:33:12.905 --> 00:33:15.825
It's possible the killer used
chicken blood to cover up human blood.

00:33:19.705 --> 00:33:21.625
Officer Qu, we're done.

00:33:23.145 --> 00:33:24.625
Alright. Wrap it up.

00:33:24.705 --> 00:33:26.585
Take him back for a statement.

00:33:39.625 --> 00:33:42.225
Officer Ran, let's go.

00:33:43.905 --> 00:33:46.185
You go ahead. I'll collect some samples.

00:34:02.905 --> 00:34:05.225
Officer He. Take it easy.

00:34:05.305 --> 00:34:06.385
Easy?

00:34:06.985 --> 00:34:08.105
I'm innocent, really.

00:34:08.185 --> 00:34:09.505
Get in the car.

00:34:09.585 --> 00:34:11.185
Eighteen chickens, you know?

00:34:11.744 --> 00:34:13.865
I handpicked each of them
and raised them myself.

00:34:13.945 --> 00:34:15.425
Don't try anything silly.

00:34:15.505 --> 00:34:17.225
Now they're dead for no reason.

00:34:17.824 --> 00:34:18.905
You guys get in first.

00:34:18.985 --> 00:34:20.784
You'd better get to the bottom of this.

00:34:21.385 --> 00:34:24.264
Otherwise, I'm staying
at the station and not leaving.

00:34:24.344 --> 00:34:25.264
Get in.

00:34:28.025 --> 00:34:31.025
Qu, this case is perfect for you.

00:34:31.625 --> 00:34:35.105
Make sure you dig into it properly
and give Mr. Ge a satisfactory answer.

00:34:36.105 --> 00:34:37.744
This case suits you too.

00:34:37.824 --> 00:34:39.784
He's in handcuffs? Must be serious.

00:34:41.145 --> 00:34:42.385
Looks like your temporary transfer
is getting extended.

00:34:43.625 --> 00:34:44.905
Will you even make it back?

00:34:46.025 --> 00:34:48.425
Well. You're just jealous.

00:34:48.505 --> 00:34:49.744
I'm good at what I do.

00:34:49.824 --> 00:34:51.505
I can crack any case in a day,
however tough it is.

00:34:52.985 --> 00:34:54.025
Han.

00:34:54.105 --> 00:34:54.945
Shouhu.

00:34:55.025 --> 00:34:57.545
Clear out my desk in six days.

00:34:57.625 --> 00:34:59.825
I'll be back on time,
just like Hong Kong, China.

00:35:00.545 --> 00:35:02.425
"Good at what I do"? Even
your own apprentice doesn't trust you.

00:35:03.385 --> 00:35:05.785
He called me when something happened.

00:35:13.305 --> 00:35:19.025
POLICE BY THE PEOPLE
FOR THE PEOPLE

00:35:21.505 --> 00:35:22.585
FORENSIC EVIDENCE INTAKE

00:35:22.665 --> 00:35:23.505
Sign here.

00:35:23.585 --> 00:35:27.025
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT EVIDENCE
TRANSFER FORM, SUBMITTED BY HE YUANHANG

00:35:36.905 --> 00:35:38.905
SUBMITTED BY RAN FANGXU

00:35:40.705 --> 00:35:42.825
Run the tests as soon as possible.
I'll treat you to a meal later.

00:35:47.065 --> 00:35:50.385
I told you. If you dress so elegantly,
you won't catch criminals.

00:35:57.065 --> 00:36:00.105
Why are you still standing there?
The suspect's been arrested.

00:36:00.185 --> 00:36:01.625
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT

00:36:05.625 --> 00:36:06.785
NOTEBOOK

00:36:06.865 --> 00:36:10.545
FORENSIC DEPARTMENT
INTERROGATION ROOM

00:36:12.025 --> 00:36:17.225
LENIENCY FOR CONFESSION
SEVERITY FOR RESISTANCE

00:36:17.305 --> 00:36:20.705
Wolfie, we've known
each other a long time.

00:36:20.785 --> 00:36:22.945
I won't need to repeat the rules, right?

00:36:23.025 --> 00:36:24.665
No.

00:36:28.545 --> 00:36:29.625
Take a look at this.

00:36:30.225 --> 00:36:31.225
Start from the beginning.

00:36:31.305 --> 00:36:33.225
Who are these two? Where did they go?

00:36:38.065 --> 00:36:39.265
MISSING PERSONS

00:36:43.785 --> 00:36:47.785
Officer, if you're asking me,
who am I supposed to ask?

00:36:47.865 --> 00:36:49.265
I honestly don't know.

00:36:51.745 --> 00:36:53.905
Alright. That's enough.

00:36:56.745 --> 00:36:57.905
Wrap it up and leave.

00:36:58.825 --> 00:37:01.585
Officer He, what are you doing?

00:37:01.665 --> 00:37:03.465
Don't be mad.

00:37:03.545 --> 00:37:06.065
I'll talk. I'll talk, alright?

00:37:57.785 --> 00:38:00.745
Ten thousand in cash upfront.
Another 30,000 after it's done.

00:38:01.385 --> 00:38:03.985
The cigarettes are a little extra for you.

00:38:07.225 --> 00:38:09.105
You want them laid out or tied up?

00:38:09.945 --> 00:38:11.425
I want them gone.